类 VObj

java.lang.Object
P2V.VObj
直接已知子类:
SubViewer, VElps, VImg, VLine, VPoly, VRect, VText
public abstract class VObj extends Object
VObj is an abstract class that serves as a base for all visual objects in the application. It provides a number of properties that are common to all visual objects, such as position, width, height, fill color, stroke color, stroke weight, and an id.
作者:
Telsa
